efiscen_tools.gis.io

Class RasterIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • efiscen_tools.gis.io.RasterIO

  • public class RasterIO
extends java.lang.Object
    Handles loading and saving rasters. Stores information about raster sizes and coordinate systems. Stage of development - just first prototype ;)
